snippet.textDisplay: The flute seems to be completely masked in the mix and is barely audible. With better mixing, it could have stood out more effectively. While the drums, guitars, keys, dhol, bamboo clap, and gogona are all mixed quite well, the flute shouldn’t be so dominated, as it brings a natural and organic tone that adds depth and emotion to the song.
snippet.textOriginal: The flute seems to be completely masked in the mix and is barely audible. With better mixing, it could have stood out more effectively. While the drums, guitars, keys, dhol, bamboo clap, and gogona are all mixed quite well, the flute shouldn’t be so dominated, as it brings a natural and organic tone that adds depth and emotion to the song.
